                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. As I was taking the prisoner to the watchhouse to lock him up, he said, it is dirty work; they may transport me, and do what they like.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181209160066"></xptr> Prisoner's Defence. The gentleman asked me what I had got about me. I said, nothing I went in immediately. He searched me, and found nothing.</p>
               <p>GUILTY, aged 49,</p>
